ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
SubjectMarine Spark-ignition Engine, Vessel and Off-road Recreational Vehicle Emission Regulations
PrecisMARINE SPARK-IGNITION ENGINE, VESSEL AND OFF-ROAD RECREATIONAL VEHICLE EMISSION REGULATIONS, in order to reduce smog-forming emissions such as HC, NOx, CO and other pollutants listed as toxic substances in Schedule 1 of CEPA 1999, from marine spark-ignition engines, vessels and off-road recreational vehicles.
